@PosLajuWebhookCapture_HostAddress = http://localhost:5079
@Password = changeme

### Health check (gated behind the shared secret)
GET {{PosLajuWebhookCapture_HostAddress}}/health
X-Password: {{Password}}

### Capture a PosLaju webhook (body + headers stored verbatim, always 200)
POST {{PosLajuWebhookCapture_HostAddress}}/poslaju
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "account_no": "ACC123456",
  "tracking_number": "ELM123456789MY",
  "event_code": "LM_SUCCESS",
  "date_time": "2026-06-18 14:30:00"
}

### Process all unprocessed captured events
POST {{PosLajuWebhookCapture_HostAddress}}/process
X-Password: {{Password}}
